{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Express 웹서버 만들기 (1)"},"html":"<h1 id=\"express-프레임워크---1-nodejs\"><a href=\"#express-%ED%94%84%EB%A0%88%EC%9E%84%EC%9B%8C%ED%81%AC---1-nodejs\" aria-label=\"express 프레임워크   1 nodejs permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Express 프레임워크 - 1 (Node.js)</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>웹 &#x26; 모바일을 위한 Node.js 기반 웹 어플리케이션 프레임 워크</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"서버-만들기\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"서버 만들기 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>서버 만들기</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>node.js 설치 필수</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"프로젝트-구조\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0\" aria-label=\"프로젝트 구조 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>프로젝트 구조</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Project&gt;\n- app.js\n- package.json  // npm init -y 명령어로 생성</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"express-모듈-설치\"><a href=\"#express-%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%88-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"express 모듈 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Express 모듈 설치</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&gt; npm install express --save\n&amp; yarn add express\n--&gt;\n&lt;Project&gt;\n- node_modules\n- app.js\n- package.json\n...</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"서버-구동-코드-간단하게\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84-%EA%B5%AC%EB%8F%99-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%EA%B0%84%EB%8B%A8%ED%95%98%EA%B2%8C\" aria-label=\"서버 구동 코드 간단하게 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>서버 구동 코드 간단하게</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">// app.js\nvar express = require(&#39;express&#39;);\n\nvar app = express();\n\napp.listen(3000);</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><em>require</em> 는 Node.js에서 javascript모듈을 호출하기 위한 함수이다.</li>\n<li>\n<h2 id=\"express-모듈을-호출-3000번-포트로-서버가-구동된다\"><a href=\"#express-%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%88%EC%9D%84-%ED%98%B8%EC%B6%9C-3000%EB%B2%88-%ED%8F%AC%ED%8A%B8%EB%A1%9C-%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84%EA%B0%80-%EA%B5%AC%EB%8F%99%EB%90%9C%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"express 모듈을 호출 3000번 포트로 서버가 구동된다 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>express 모듈을 호출, 3000번 포트로 서버가 구동된다.</h2>\n<h3 id=\"요청--응답-간단한게\"><a href=\"#%EC%9A%94%EC%B2%AD--%EC%9D%91%EB%8B%B5-%EA%B0%84%EB%8B%A8%ED%95%9C%EA%B2%8C\" aria-label=\"요청  응답 간단한게 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>요청 &#x26; 응답 간단한게</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">// app.js\nvar express = require(&#39;express&#39;);</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>var app = express();</p>\n<p>app.get('/', function(req, res) {\nres.send('Hello World!!');\n});</p>\n<p>app.get('/json', function(req, res) {\nres.json({\nid: 1,\nname: 'Tom'\n});\n});</p>\n<p>app.listen(3000);</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">- _http://localhost:3000_ 으로 접속시</code></pre></div>\n<p>Hello World!!</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">- _http://localhost:3000/json_ 으로 접속시</code></pre></div>\n<p>{\nid: 1,\nname: 'Tom'\n}</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">---\n### ejs 뷰 엔진 적용</code></pre></div>\n<p>// ejs 모듈 설치</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>npm install ejs --save\n&#x26; yarn add ejs</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>// 프로젝트 구조</p>\n<Project>\n- node_modules\n- views\n-- index.ejs\n- app.js\n- package.json\n~~~\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">// app.js\n\nvar path = require(&#39;path&#39;); \n...\napp.set(&#39;views&#39;, path.join(__dirname, &#39;views&#39;));\napp.set(&#39;view engine&#39;, &#39;ejs&#39;);\n\napp.get(&#39;/render&#39;, function(req, res) {\n    res.render(&#39;index&#39;, { message: &#39;Hello World!&#39; });\n});\n...</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">// views/index.ejs\n\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\n&lt;html&gt;\n&lt;head&gt;\n    &lt;meta charset=&quot;UTF-8&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;title&gt;Document&lt;/title&gt;\n&lt;/head&gt;\n&lt;body&gt;\n    &lt;%= message %&gt;\n&lt;/body&gt;\n&lt;/html&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><em>/render</em> 로 요청했을 시 <em>index.ejs</em> 를 응답</li>\n<li>두번째 파라미터에 렌더링될 데이터 추가</li>\n<li>&#x3C;% %> 형식로 렌더링 및 javascript 문법 사용</li>\n</ul>","headings":[{"value":"Express 프레임워크 - 1 (Node.js)","depth":1},{"value":"서버 만들기","depth":2},{"value":"프로젝트 구조","depth":3},{"value":"Express 모듈 설치","depth":3},{"value":"서버 구동 코드 간단하게","depth":3},{"value":"express 모듈을 호출, 3000번 포트로 서버가 구동된다.","depth":2},{"value":"요청 & 응답 간단한게","depth":3}]}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/blog/node-express/2018-06-09-ExpressJS-1/","previous":{"node":{"id":"9e808265-0838-5e0a-b745-e67e99ac52cb","frontmatter":{"title":"Express에 Sequelize 적용해보기","category":"node-express","date":"2018-06-09"},"fields":{"slug":"/posts/blog/node-express/2018-06-09-Express-&-Sequelize/"}}},"next":{"node":{"id":"f3b5ba94-e765-525a-baf9-dd02e2ce55aa","frontmatter":{"title":"null과 undefined의 차이점","category":"javascript","date":"2018-06-16"},"fields":{"slug":"/posts/blog/javascript/2018-06-16-Javascript의-null-vs-undefined/"}}}}}